                                        <p>it get u all available products with that category </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-xl-4 d-flex align-items-stretch" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                                    <div class="icon-box mt-4 mt-xl-0">
